headline: Dell Technologies Lifts Long-Term Targets, Mizuho Sees AI Upside Potential
summary: Dell Technologies Inc. (NYSE:DELL) is one of the AI Stocks In The Spotlight For Investors. On October 8, Mizuho raised its price target on the stock to $170 from $160 while maintaining an Outperform rating. The rating affirmation follows Dell’s Analyst Day in New York City.
